          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Psychic Power" typeId="9060-973c-99e9-75b4">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if that Psychic Test had two or more dice with the same results, the nearest visible enemy unit within 27&quot; suffers 3D3 SW.</characteristic>
