      <profiles>
        <profile name="Fickle Grasp" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="1502-5222-acbb-cc01">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">This unit cannot capture objectives.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Summoned Horror" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="0dcf-a26f-713a-583d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit&apos;s End step, take another turn. If you have another unit with this ability and ready, you must select that unit to Activate.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink name="Daemonic" id="c5cf-019f-c0bf-2a22" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="3b9e-8b58-9bed-fb98"/>
      </infoLinks>
    </selectionEntry>
  </sharedSelectionEntries>
  <sharedRules>
    <rule name="Daemonic" id="3b9e-8b58-9bed-fb98" hidden="false">
      <description>For each attack that targets this unit, the Wound Roll of that attack is always successful on a 5+ and always fails on any result worse than 5+.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Entwined Will" id="5a20-9748-a65b-7e1f" hidden="false">
      <description>While this unit is not active, if your active unit with Psyker is within 9” of one or more units with Entwined Will, for each Psychic Test that unit makes, add 1 D6 to that Psychic Test.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Inferno" id="188a-b70b-b086-9c0e" hidden="false">
      <description>While any of your units with Psyker are within 9” of this unit, each of this weapon’s attacks gain Pierce and Shred.</description>
    </rule>
  </sharedRules>
  <selectionEntries>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Relics (Reference)" hidden="false" id="d99e-9556-c5f6-0407" sortIndex="3">
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="f5e5-d983-d892-9541" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="6cbb-cba9-064d-978c-min" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="6cbb-cba9-064d-978c-max" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Configuration" hidden="false" id="8c12-fc52-3844-1e0d" targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="1 Dust Aegis" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="680a-7c95-55fa-ef82">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">This unit gains Resilient 5+</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="2 Siphoning Sigil" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="f2b2-9452-7098-7d53">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">For each Psychic Test this unit makes, add 1 D6 to the Psychic Test for each other unit with Psyker on the battlefield. For each Psychic Test an enemy unit makes while within 12” of this unit, that unit&apos;s Psyker X is worsened by 1 for that Psychic Test.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3 Staff of Influence" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="37f8-515f-c8ad-7d58">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit gains this ability or Activates, roll XD6 where X is this unit’s Psyker X. Keep each dice as your ‘influence dice’. While any of your units have ability, for each attack that targets this unit, instead of making a Saving Throw for that attack, you may ‘spend influence’. To spend influence, discard one of those influence dice equal to or greater than the result for that Saving Throw to be successful.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 Unholy Ammunition" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="87b7-363e-8ccf-df89">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">For each attack this unit makes with a weapon with Inferno, on a Wound Roll of 5+ for that attack, the target unit suffers X SW where X is the Damage of that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6 Tablet of Treason" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="094e-964e-533c-405a">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit finishes a March, it may make a Psychic Test. If it does, select an enemy infantry unit visible to and within X” of this unit, where X is the total result of that Psychic Test. The selected unit’s non-leader models make ranged attacks and you select the targets for those attacks.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5 Trespassers’ Ring" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="0aed-2950-6019-dced">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After an enemy unit finishes a March visible to this unit, you may roll a D6. On a 5+, this unit may Fall Back up to 9&quot; (instead of its normal M), and may move through enemy models and terrain as if they were not there while doing so.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink name="Resilient (X)" id="43bd-d1b8-ce34-1ed1" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="253c-c1fa-d29d-d21e"/>
      </infoLinks>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Psychic Powers (Reference)" hidden="false" id="0171-0833-7fc4-972d" sortIndex="2">
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="2961-1d3e-4adf-052e" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="3818-5dec-525f-9143-min" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="3818-5dec-525f-9143-max" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Configuration" hidden="false" id="f360-8a68-627a-fe58" targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="1 Psychic Subjugation" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="e9cf-3e6f-ea5c-76e7">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select an enemy unit within 16&quot;. The selected unit suffers XD3+1 Suppression where X is this unit’s Psyker X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="2 Destiny&apos;s Doorstep" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="989b-95ed-8fbb-e4e1">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">If this unit is in reserves, roll 3D6. You may Deploy it at last X” away from all enemy units where X is the result. Otherwise, this unit may Fall Back up to 9&quot; (instead of its normal M), and may move over terrain and models as if they were not there while doing so.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3 Temporal Manipulation" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="de1e-1879-559a-5b39">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select a friendly unit within 9” of this model. Select and apply one of the following effects:


a) After the next time you roll for initiative, the selected unit Heals XD3 where X is this unit’s Psyker X.
b) The selected unit Heals X where X is this unit&apos;s Psyker X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 Tzeentch’s Labyrinth" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="fcd2-d13d-fa07-9cb0">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select up to one debris terrain piece within 18” of this unit. Remove the selected debris from the battlefield. Then, place the debris anywhere on the battlefield. Do not place it on any terrain, objectives, or models. After moving that terrain, each enemy unit within 3” of that terrain suffers X SW where X is this unit’s Psyker X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5 Bolt of Change" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="9351-c256-d375-0321">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select one visible enemy unit within 16&quot; of this model. It suffers XD3+1 SW where X is this unit’s Psyker X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Psychic Powers (Reference)" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="84e8-17b2-6a57-120c">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">1 Psychic Subjugation: Select an enemy unit within 18”. The selected unit suffers 2D3+X Suppression where X is this unit’s Psyker X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6 Immolating Vortex" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="6317-f3a9-67ef-7902">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select any point on the battlefield within 16&quot; of and visible to this unit. Each enemy unit within XD6” of the selected point, where X is the number of times this psychic power has been Cast this battle, suffers 2 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Army Rules (Reference)" hidden="false" id="368e-26e3-98ff-35c3" sortIndex="1">
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="b528-3219-0b8f-35b1" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="fa8a-f266-43e2-48fc-min" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="fa8a-f266-43e2-48fc-max" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Configuration" hidden="false" id="c0fe-5b1b-b5ff-cefe" targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Entwined Will" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="eb32-15f5-befc-e96e">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit is not active, if your active unit with Psyker is within 9” of one or more units with Entwined Will, for each Psychic Test that unit makes, add 1 D6 to that Psychic Test.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Daemonic" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="d87d-c93b-77b5-aedd">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each attack that targets this unit, the Wound Roll of that attack is always successful on a 5+ and always fails on any result worse than 5+.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Great Traitors’ Arsenal" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="e6b2-19e6-5d3f-258d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">You may also add units to your army list from the “Chaos Space Marines” document. (will add when 3.0 CSM is added, DM me if i forget)</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Inferno" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="106b-f1d2-35eb-d344">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While any of your units with Psyker are within 9” of this unit, each of this weapon’s attacks gain Pierce and Shred.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
