        <profile name="Roaring Distortion" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="89e2-c6c0-eab5-8f6e">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if there is a friendly SUMMONED FLAMERS unit on the battlefield, add 1 SUMMONED FLAMERS model to that unit. Otherwise, create a SUMMONED FLAMERS unit within 1” of this unit outside of the engagement range of enemy units with 1 model. That unit is ready.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Manifest Tutelaries" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="5159-2f30-264b-b0e1">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if there is a friendly SUMMONED SCREAMERS unit on the battlefield, add 1 SUMMONED SCREAMERS model to that unit. Otherwise, create a SUMMONED SCREAMERS unit within 1” of this unit outside of the engagement range of enemy units with 1 model. That unit is ready.</characteristic>
