          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After any unit Activates, if this unit has one or more SCARAB OCCULT TERMINATORS models, until the End step, this unit gains Resilient 6+.</characteristic>
