        <profile name="Impossible Knowledge" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="9810-d2de-1975-fc40">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit Casts, choose one of the following effects:


Change Lightning: Select a visible enemy unit within 9” and roll 3D3. That roll is X. Then, select a second enemy unit within X&quot; of and visible to the first, and a third within X&quot; of and visible to the second, and so on for any number of enemy units. Each enemy unit can only be selected once, and you can stop selecting at any time. Then, each selected unit suffers 2 SW.


Chaos Familiars: Select either:
a) SUMMONED FLAMERS with 2 models
b) SUMMONED SCREAMERS with 3 models
c) SUMMONED PINK HORRORS with 2 models
d) SUMMONED CHAOS SPAWN OF TZEENTCH with 1 model
Create the selected unit within 3” of this unit. That unit is ready.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Disk of Tzeentch" typeId="3ce5-e1a1-5b1f-0410" typeName="Wargear" hidden="false" id="dd83-df1d-b8ab-5d01">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="14c0-3a47-fe6d-6563">After this unit’s Attacks step, it may Fall Back.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
