        <profile name="Warp Vortex" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="3583-594a-42e6-aa27">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Move step, it loses whichever of the following abilities it has if any, then roll a D3 and this unit gains the following ability equal to the result:


1. Reality Transposition: After this unit gains this ability, this unit may Fall Back up to 9+D6&quot; (instead of its M). During this move, you may move through terrain and models as if they were not there.


2. Wyrding Aurora: After this unit’s Move step, all units within 9” of this unit suffer D6+1 SW.


3. Beam of Unreality: After this unit’s Move step, select a visible enemy unit within 18&quot; of this unit. Draw a line between the selected unit and this unit. The selected unit and each unit that line passes over suffers D6+1 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Mutalith Claws" typeId="2dff-53d0-6d25-8c59" typeName="Weapon" hidden="false" id="3681-8c74-c6e5-ae47">
          <characteristics>
